f=Engineering/dev/custom/delivery-governance/assets/execution-plan-template.md · h1:Execution Plan [agent] [task id] [date]=Rail artifact. Written acting agent BEFORE any external tool call; frozen hashed quinn (plan-lock). mid-run tool call derivable document halts agent escalates. Append-only once locked changed plan NEW plan citing one. · h2:1. Task=**Requested by:** [operator agent reference], **Objective:** [one sentence what run produces], **In scope:** [systems/files/data run touch], **Out scope:** [explicitly touched deviation tripwires] · h2:Planned tool calls (ordered)=\| # \| Tool \| Purpose \| Argument shape (not secrets) \| Expected effect \| · h2:Planned tool calls (ordered)=\|---\|------\|---------\|------------------------------\|-----------------\| · h2:Planned tool calls (ordered)=\| 1 \| <FILL_IN> \| <FILL_IN> \| <FILL_IN> \| <FILL_IN> \| · h2:Planned tool calls (ordered)=Argument *shape*, literal values they contain secrets. Conditional branches listed numbered alternatives ("3a 3b"), never left implicit. · h2:3. Data touched=**Reads:** [sources, config grants], **Writes:** NONE agent-executed destructive create/update/delete becomes prepared script operator (Rail 3). List prepared scripts here., **Egress:** [allowlisted destinations Rail anything else fails closed] · h2:4. Stop conditions=[conditions under which agent halts instead proceeding unexpected state, missing grant, off-plan need], Default: any needed call HALT, escalate quinn; improvise. · h2:Lock block (quinn fills)=**Plan hash:** [hash], **Locked at:** [timestamp] **Locked by:** quinn, **Supersedes plan:** [id none], **Outcome:** [completed on-plan halted step reason superseded plan id]